      "span_text": "Expanding the scope of a previous analysis to include both wider geographical coverage and the views of HCWs who work closely with pregnant women reinforces several findings from a previously published study on pregnant women in Jharkhand alone [CITATION_1] , while bringing to light a number of important differences and areas for potential action."
